676
00:51:23,050 --> 00:51:25,700
You must bring me something in return.

677
00:51:25,800 --> 00:51:28,650
- What?
- A gun.

678
00:51:28,750 --> 00:51:30,750
- A gun?
- A very special gun.

679
00:51:30,850 --> 00:51:34,100
Designed by the greatest
computer ever invented.

680
00:51:34,200 --> 00:51:37,200
But the only way to find it
is to go to Magrathea.

681
00:51:37,300 --> 00:51:41,700
Fine. I'll get your gun.
Just give me the coordinates.

682
00:51:41,800 --> 00:51:44,600
And what will you give me
to ensure your return?

683
00:51:45,500 --> 00:51:47,850
My word as President.

684
00:51:49,200 --> 00:51:52,650
No. I need a hostage.

685
00:51:55,200 --> 00:52:02,350
Only... what does Zaphod
Beeblebrox treasure?

686
00:52:06,000 --> 00:52:07,000
Come on.

687
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:12,500
Oh, no!

688
00:52:13,150 --> 00:52:15,900
Hey, hey, hey! Take it easy now.
Think about this before you do.

689
00:52:16,000 --> 00:52:19,200
No, stop it! Oh, that kind of tickles.

690
00:52:19,300 --> 00:52:22,800
Two heads are better than one.
Double your pleasure.

691
00:52:22,900 --> 00:52:26,700
It's not fair! You need me!

692
00:52:26,850 --> 00:52:31,000
Come back! Come back!
Don't leave me alone.

693
00:52:34,500 --> 00:52:35,950
<i>Come back!</i>

694
00:52:36,100 --> 00:52:37,700
Well, now, that was fun, wasn't it?

694
00:52:37,800 --> 00:52:39,000
And there I was thinking I was the only one

695
00:52:39,100 --> 00:52:41,200
who considered your boyfriend
a narcissistic moron,

695
00:52:41,300 --> 00:52:42,650
when apparently the whole galaxy does!

696
00:52:42,750 --> 00:52:45,550
What about you?
"Oh, excuse me, Mr. Humma, sir.

697
00:52:45,650 --> 00:52:49,000
"We're not actually with him.
We just came here to worship you."

698
00:52:49,100 --> 00:52:53,000
- Very brave!
- Where the hell is Ford?

699
00:52:56,150 --> 00:53:02,700
By the left, march.
Left, right, left, right, left, right.

700
00:53:02,800 --> 00:53:07,000
Mr. President, we're here for your protection.

701
00:53:07,500 --> 00:53:10,750
Fire upon the kidnapper.

702
00:53:10,850 --> 00:53:12,200
<i>Hey, come on!</i>

703
00:53:12,300 --> 00:53:14,900
