706
00:53:21,850 --> 00:53:24,250
Thank you, darling. I'll be in touch.

707
00:53:29,500 --> 00:53:31,000
Come on, Zaphod.

708
00:53:35,500 --> 00:53:38,250
- Hey, hey, what did I miss?
- What the hell have you been doing?!

709
00:53:38,350 --> 00:53:39,900
I was out doing field research.

709
00:53:40,000 --> 00:53:41,800
So, they found where we are.
Belgium bummer!

710
00:53:41,900 --> 00:53:44,500
Bummer? They're shooting at us!
What are we gonna do?

711
00:53:44,600 --> 00:53:45,600
I have an idea.

711
00:53:45,700 --> 00:53:48,050
Does it involve pushing him out there
and running the other way?

712
00:53:48,150 --> 00:53:50,600
What? He's the one they want.

713
00:53:50,700 --> 00:53:53,000
Tricia, you can't go out there.
What are you doing?

714
00:53:54,250 --> 00:53:57,250
- Back off!
- What's going on?

715
00:53:58,900 --> 00:54:02,150
<i>I have the President
and I will kill him, I swear I will.</i>

716
00:54:02,250 --> 00:54:06,250
- Could that actually kill him?
- I don't think so.

717
00:54:06,350 --> 00:54:08,500
- It's an aerosol can.
- Oh.

718
00:54:08,600 --> 00:54:12,100
Okay, frightened now, frightened.

719
00:54:12,750 --> 00:54:16,200
- Hi, little guy.
- Get her!

720
00:54:16,300 --> 00:54:19,300
- Zaphod, no, come on!
- Arthur!

721
00:54:20,100 --> 00:54:22,900
- Arthur!
- Tricia!

722
00:54:23,000 --> 00:54:26,000
- Arthur!
- Tricia! Wait!

723
00:54:34,950 --> 00:54:37,000
Arthur!

724
00:54:40,200 --> 00:54:44,100
<b>Resistance is useless!</b>

725
00:54:53,200 --> 00:54:56,900
<i>Bring her to Vogsphere
for processing, captain.</i>

726
00:54:58,700 --> 00:55:00,450
Circus? Circus?

727
00:55:00,550 --> 00:55:03,150
They got her and it's my fault.
We have to go. Let's go!

728
00:55:03,250 --> 00:55:04,750
Let's go!

729
00:55:08,500 --> 00:55:10,350
Computer, take us to Magrathea!

730
00:55:10,450 --> 00:55:12,850
What? No, no, no, no, no.
We've got to go after Tricia.

731
00:55:12,950 --> 00:55:14,400
- Who?
- Trillian, Trillian!

732
00:55:14,500 --> 00:55:18,000
They've got Trillian,
you stupid half-brained git!

733
00:55:18,100 --> 00:55:21,200
Right, you're coming out!

734
00:55:21,300 --> 00:55:25,200
Computer, we don't want to go to
Magrathea yet. We want to follow the ships.

735
00:55:25,300 --> 00:55:28,950
<i>Oh, I'd love to, fella, but, wouldn't you know it,
