736
00:55:29,050 --> 00:55:30,150
Oh, come on!

737
00:55:30,250 --> 00:55:32,500
<i>I'm sorry about that, but it wasn't my fault.</i>

738
00:55:32,600 --> 00:55:34,800
What are you doing on this spaceship?

739
00:55:34,900 --> 00:55:36,500
- Ford?
- Marvin.

740
00:55:36,600 --> 00:55:39,000
