741
00:55:39,100 --> 00:55:40,400
And?

742
00:55:40,850 --> 00:55:42,400
It hates me.

743
00:55:42,750 --> 00:55:45,700
No, uh-uh. Eddie, computer...

744
00:55:45,800 --> 00:55:49,300
