745
00:55:49,400 --> 00:55:53,850
<i>Activating Emergency Escape Pod.
It's super-neat and fun to fly!</i>

747
00:55:56,300 --> 00:55:57,750
Unbelievable!

748
00:55:57,850 --> 00:55:59,100
I'm in. I'm in.

748
00:55:59,300 --> 00:56:01,100
- Okay, Ford!
- Yeah, I'm here.

748
00:56:01,200 --> 00:56:02,200
