749
00:56:02,300 --> 00:56:03,900
- Okay, we'll press this button here.
- Okay, okay.

750
00:56:04,000 --> 00:56:05,900
Oh, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.

751
00:56:06,000 --> 00:56:08,000
- Press this button again.
- No. Nothing's...

751
00:56:08,100 --> 00:56:09,200
