752
00:56:09,300 --> 00:56:12,250
- Good man, good man, good man.

752
00:56:09,300 --> 00:56:10,300
- Good move.

752
00:56:10,400 --> 00:56:12,300
- Okay. No, no! Not now!

753
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:13,900
Okay, we're wobbling.

753
00:56:14,000 --> 00:56:15,900
- Hey, you forgot your towel.
- No!

754
00:56:16,000 --> 00:56:18,550
Get him off me! I'll kill him! I'll kill...

755
00:56:18,650 --> 00:56:21,150
- Okay, Ford, there's a...
- Is that better?

756
00:56:21,300 --> 00:56:23,250
No, that's worse, that's worse.

757
00:56:23,350 --> 00:56:25,500
- Do what... I don't need that.
- No, no, no.

757
00:56:25,600 --> 00:56:26,700
- I don't need that.
- Okay.

758
00:56:26,800 --> 00:56:29,450
Can you stop the rocking?
Okay, Marvin, any ideas?

759
00:56:29,550 --> 00:56:33,200
I have a million ideas.
