810
01:01:20,450 --> 01:01:23,650
No, Tricia Marie McMillan of Earth.

811
01:01:23,800 --> 01:01:25,350
Oh, right.

812
01:01:31,000 --> 01:01:35,300
Sorry, no record of Earth.

813
01:01:35,400 --> 01:01:39,200
Galactic sector ZZ9 Plural Z Alpha?

814
01:01:39,350 --> 01:01:42,750
- Oh, yes.
- She's lying.

815
01:01:44,250 --> 01:01:47,600
She's skinny, and she's pretty,
