for a hyperspace expressway.

821
01:02:14,500 --> 01:02:18,000
Who in their right mind gives
an order to destroy a planet?

822
01:02:20,100 --> 01:02:24,100
- He said the gray building, right?
- All the buildings are gray.

823
01:02:24,200 --> 01:02:27,500
"Give me a hand." Ha-ha, very funny.

824
01:02:27,600 --> 01:02:31,100
How am I supposed to drive this pod
with one arm? Stupid human.

825
01:02:35,700 --> 01:02:38,700
So, you need to go back and fill that in.

826
01:02:38,800 --> 01:02:40,100
And then, make sure,

826
01:02:40,200 --> 01:02:42,100
- when you fill in the facilitating form...
- Okay.

827
01:02:42,200 --> 01:02:47,050
Leave this to me. I'm British.
I know how to queue.

828
01:02:49,000 --> 01:02:51,050
If you'd fill that form in for me,

829
01:02:51,150 --> 01:02:53,850
