830
01:02:53,950 --> 01:02:57,000
You'll find writing implements to your left...

830
01:02:57,100 --> 01:02:58,300
You're President. Can you do anything?

831
01:02:58,400 --> 01:03:01,200
Presidents don't have power.
Their job is to draw attention away from it.

831
01:03:01,300 --> 01:03:04,000
- No offense. You're a great guy.
- Hey!

832
01:03:05,350 --> 01:03:07,400
Hey, how're you doin'?

833
01:03:07,500 --> 01:03:09,000
Hey, it's me, your President!

833
01:03:09,100 --> 01:03:12,200
What's goin' on? Nice to see you.
Thanks for coming.

834
01:03:12,300 --> 01:03:15,100
All right. I know that sponge. All right!

835
01:03:15,200 --> 01:03:17,500
- Next!
- President coming through.

836
01:03:17,600 --> 01:03:20,650
How you doin', Pinhead?
Thank you. No, really, it's me.

837
01:03:21,550 --> 01:03:23,350
I love kabuki. Look at that little thing.

838
01:03:23,450 --> 01:03:26,350
Out the way. Out the way.

839
01:03:27,150 --> 01:03:29,450
Give us a kiss! Give us a kiss, darling!

840
01:03:30,500 --> 01:03:33,400
Hi, I've come about release of a prisoner.

841
