846
01:03:51,300 --> 01:03:54,600
Now, according to the Galactic Penal Code,

847
01:03:54,700 --> 01:03:59,450
- the punishment for a presidential kidnapping...
- Come on, love!

848
01:03:59,550 --> 01:04:03,300
