Bugblatter Beast of Traal.

849
01:04:04,150 --> 01:04:06,150
Good day.

850
01:04:07,700 --> 01:04:09,000
Get off of me!

851
01:04:10,000 --> 01:04:12,700
What the hell is that?

852
01:04:12,800 --> 01:04:18,000
No! wait, wait!
There's been some kind of mistake.

853
01:04:20,250 --> 01:04:25,850
- Tick all the boxes at the right-hand side
of the page. - Okay. Right. Yeah, I've got it.

854
01:04:25,950 --> 01:04:27,950
- Uh-huh.
- Not that one!

855
01:04:28,050 --> 01:04:32,350
<i>What to do if you find yourself
stuck with no hope of rescue.</i>

856
01:04:32,450 --> 01:04:36,750
<i>Consider how lucky you are that
life has been good to you so far.</i>

857
01:04:36,850 --> 01:04:40,250
<i>Alternatively, if life hasn't
been good to you so far,</i>

858
01:04:40,350 --> 01:04:43,500
<i>which, given your current
circumstances seems more likely,</i>

859
01:04:43,600 --> 01:04:47,750
