it won't be troubling you much longer.</i>

860
01:04:51,200 --> 01:04:54,000
Right, there we go.

861
01:04:54,200 --> 01:04:56,600
Oh, kidnapping the President!

862
01:04:56,700 --> 01:05:01,100
And, no, she's not eligible
