That was one of mine.
I got an award for it.

1117
01:25:41,650 --> 01:25:45,150
All right, Frank? That's... that's Frank.

1118
01:25:46,100 --> 01:25:50,500
Ah-ha. They've nearly finished the oceans.

1119
01:25:59,000 --> 01:26:00,350
Zaphod.

1120
01:26:00,450 --> 01:26:02,450
Here, it's...

1121
01:26:04,950 --> 01:26:08,000
It's just like Humma said.

1122
01:26:08,100 --> 01:26:09,900
Now you can go get your head back.

1122
01:26:10,000 --> 01:26:10,900
- Hey, Ford.
- Hey.

1123
01:26:11,000 --> 01:26:13,250
It's been nice knowing you,
you zarking frood.

1124
01:26:13,350 --> 01:26:14,350
No, no, no, no, no!

1125
01:26:14,450 --> 01:26:16,700
- Whoa!
- Lucky this is a bust too.

1126
01:26:16,800 --> 01:26:22,350
