1131
01:26:33,400 --> 01:26:35,900
Fantastic. Fantastic.

1132
01:26:37,050 --> 01:26:39,700
<i>That is, if you point it at someone
and pull the trigger,</i>

1133
01:26:39,800 --> 01:26:42,700
