1134
01:26:42,850 --> 01:26:44,800
Give me that thing.

1135
01:26:44,900 --> 01:26:46,850
<i>It was designed by Deep Thought,</i>

1136
01:26:46,950 --> 01:26:50,800
<i>but commissioned by a consortium
